snippet: The top-ranked Baylor women, the defending national champion, lost for the first time since the 2011 N.C.A.A. tournament.
abstract: College Basketball Women's Roundup; Stanford defeats Baylor, 71-69, ending Baylor's 42-game winning streak; other women's and men's scores noted.
lead_paragraph: The top-ranked Baylor women, the defending national champion, lost for the first time since the 2011 N.C.A.A. tournament.
